Repeat: P1 wrapping yarn twice around needle; p3
Slip 1 wyib dropping the extra wraps; k3
Drop slip stitch off needle to front of work, k2, pick up dropped stitch and knit it; k1
P1 wrapping yarn twice around needle; p3
Slip 1 wyib dropping the extra wraps; k3
sl 2 wyib; drop slip stitch off needle to front of work, slip the same 2 stitches back to left-hand needle, pick up dropped stitch and knit it; k3
